### ============================================
### 1. CREAR LIBROS (POST)
### ============================================

### 1.1 Crear Libro 1: Clean Code (JSON)
POST http://localhost:8080/softlearning/books
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Clean Code",
  "price": 35.0,
  "available": true,
  "author": "Robert C. Martin",
  "publicationDate": "2008-08-01",
  "availabilityDate": "2023-12-01",
  "weight": 0.5,
  "width": 18.0,
  "height": 24.0,
  "depth": 2.0,
  "isFragile": false
}

### 1.2 Crear Libro 2: Don Quijote de la Mancha (XML)
POST http://localhost:8080/softlearning/books
Content-Type: application/xml
Accept: application/xml

<book>
    <id>2</id>
    <name>Don Quijote de la Mancha</name>
    <price>20.99</price>
    <available>true</available>
    <author>Miguel de Cervantes</author>
    <publicationDate>1605-01-16</publicationDate>
    <availabilityDate>2024-02-01</availabilityDate>
    <weight>1.2</weight>
    <width>16.0</width>
    <height>24.0</height>
    <depth>5.0</depth>
    <isFragile>false</isFragile>
</book>

### ============================================
### 2. OBTENER LIBROS (GET)
### ============================================

### 2.1 Obtener todos los libros (JSON)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/books
Accept: application/json

### 2.2 Obtener todos los libros (XML)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/books
Accept: application/xml

### 2.3 Obtener Libro por ID 1 (JSON)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/books/1
Accept: application/json

### 2.4 Obtener Libro por ID 1 (XML)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/books/1
Accept: application/xml

### 2.5 Obtener Libro por ID 2 (JSON)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/books/2
Accept: application/json

### 2.6 Obtener Libro por ID 2 (XML)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/books/2
Accept: application/xml

### ============================================
### 3. ACTUALIZAR LIBROS (PUT)
### ============================================

### 3.1 Actualizar Libro 1: Cambiar precio y nombre (JSON)
PUT http://localhost:8080/softlearning/books/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Clean Code - Edicion Especial",
  "price": 39.99,
  "available": true,
  "author": "Robert C. Martin",
  "publicationDate": "2008-08-01",
  "availabilityDate": "2024-01-01",
  "weight": 0.5,
  "width": 18.0,
  "height": 24.0,
  "depth": 2.0,
  "isFragile": false
}

### 3.2 Actualizar Libro 2: Cambiar precio y marcar como frágil (XML)
PUT http://localhost:8080/softlearning/books/2
Content-Type: application/xml
Accept: application/xml

<book>
    <id>2</id>
    <name>Don Quijote de la Mancha - Edicion Vintage</name>
    <price>24.99</price>
    <available>true</available>
    <author>Miguel de Cervantes</author>
    <publicationDate>1605-01-16</publicationDate>
    <availabilityDate>2024-02-01</availabilityDate>
    <weight>1.2</weight>
    <width>16.0</width>
    <height>24.0</height>
    <depth>5.0</depth>
    <isFragile>true</isFragile>
</book>

### 3.3 Verificar actualización del Libro 1 (JSON)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/books/1
Accept: application/json

### 3.4 Verificar actualización del Libro 2 (JSON)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/books/2
Accept: application/json

### ============================================
### 4. BÚSQUEDAS CON FILTROS
### ============================================

### 4.1 Buscar libros por nombre: "Clean" (JSON)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/books/search?name=Clean
Accept: application/json

### 4.2 Buscar libros por autor: "Cervantes" (JSON)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/books/search?author=Cervantes
Accept: application/json

### 4.3 Buscar libros por precio máximo: 30 (JSON)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/books/search?maxPrice=30
Accept: application/json

### 4.4 Búsqueda combinada: nombre y precio máximo (XML)
GET http://localhost:8080/softlearning/books/search?name=Don&maxPrice=25
Accept: application/xml

### ============================================
### 5. ELIMINAR LIBRO (solo para prueba, no recomendado si se usa en órdenes)
### ============================================

### 5.1 Borrar libro 1
DELETE http://localhost:8080/softlearning/books/1

### 5.2 Borrar libro 2
DELETE http://localhost:8080/softlearning/books/2